x_{0}\in (X\cup Y )^{\complement} \Leftrightarrow x_{0}\not \in X \cup Y \Leftrightarrow x_{0} \not \in X \text{ and  } x_{0}\not \in Y \Leftrightarrow
\Leftrightarrow x_{0}\in X^{\complement} \text{ and  }x_{0}\in Y^{\complement} \Leftrightarrow x_{0} \in X^{\complement}\cap Y^{\complement}. 
